0.9.name: wordpress/wp-gallery-exif-reader
0.9.description: Extract EXIF information when using the gallery shortcode. This is specifically for those without access to the php_exif extension on their servers. Style by editing gallery-exif-reader.css. Debug by uncommenting add_action('loop_start', 'ec_exif_reader_debug', 1); in gallery-exif-reader.php.
